Mesh data structure 
===================

VertexType
	Edges	
	Triangles


EdgeType
	Vertices[2]
	GetTriangle				Give triangles using Vertex->Triangles


TriangleType
	Vertices[3]
	GetEdges				Computes edges from Vertex->Edges


MeshData
	AddTriangle(Vertices)	Check if triangle exists by checking Vertex->Triangle
	AddEdge(Vertices)		Check if edge exists by checking Vertex->Edges


Pseudo-code
-----------

MeshData.AddTriangle(Vertices)

 * Create Triangle-object
 * For each pair of vertices (v1, v2):
 	* Edges.append( AddEdge(v1, v2) )
 * Update Vertices with new triangle


MeshData.AddEdge(Vertices)
 * Check if edge exists:
 	* Yes: Return pointer
 	* No: Proceed
 * Create edge
 * Update Vertices with new edge 	



 